description:
The USB 2.0 Card Reader/Writer is a high speed device that will enable you to quickly transfer photos and other digital files from a variety of flash memory card formats. Compatibility includes SD, SDHC, MiniSD, MiniSDHC, MMC, rsMMC.
 
This Card Reader needs SD adapter for miniSD/HC card, microSDHC & microMMC card
title: CTCstore 10-in-1 USB 2.0 High Speed Memory Card Reader Writer for SD SDHC MiniSD MiniSDHC MMC rsMMC - Purple
